    ["T"] = "일리다리 파멸의 파편",
  },
  [10624] = {
    ["D"] = "Have you felt the cold chill? Perhaps what you thought was a hand on your shoulder? That was not your mind playing tricks on you, $r. The land is haunted. Ghosts litter the landscape, stuck here for all eternity.$B$BWould you like to see them? Are you sure about that? These types of things tend to change a person - and not for the better.$B$BVery well, I will need you to collect for me the ever-burning ash that is found near any of the fel lava pools of western Shadowmoon. Anywhere near green lava...",
    ["O"] = "어둠달 골짜기의 어둠달 마을에 있는 수석 연금술사 힐다가드가 영원히 타오르는 재 표본 15개를 가져오라고 했습니다.",
    ["T"] = "유령의 역사",
  },
  [10625] = {
